title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 707 - The Man Whom Fell Slowly
description:
[LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 708 - The Man Whom Fell Slowly [English Sub]

The final weekend of summer is upon Conan and the Shounen Tantei, but their plans are quickly changed because they witness a man being pushed off a building at 2PM exact. But the time of death is 2:10? Just what happened in those ten minutes that made such a world of difference?
